    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195130/extras/7c6363ccca0f56fcb68cc870cc5c39ad.avif?t=1761581776\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this demo, experience surviving the first six days of the game with the character Enthusiasm. Explore a planet with space landscapes that range from alien forests to arid deserts, facing unknown creatures. Collect precious resources and craft your own tools, which may be the key to survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195130/extras/c31c45c0fd5b4341f31ae46333d7ca27.poster.avif?t=1761581776\" width=660 height=201 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195130/extras/c31c45c0fd5b4341f31ae46333d7ca27.webm?t=1761581776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft tools and repair the ship using materials found on the planet. Defend yourself against hostile threats while struggling to mend your broken heart, both literally and figuratively.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Show that you can survive anywhere in the galaxy. In Kind Heart Survivors, your skills will be put to the test. Do you have what it takes to overcome challenges and thrive in an unknown world? Venture forth and find out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195130/extras/1cd19a6bc4982d1645f2af8dab894ca7.poster.avif?t=1761581776\" width=660 height=201 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195130/extras/1cd19a6bc4982d1645f2af8dab894ca7.webm?t=1761581776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> FEATURES</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploration</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inventory management</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Base building</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Item crafting</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survival</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Management of life, oxygen, and hunger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A survival game that awaits your feedback to get even better!</p>",
